title: Superman 23 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.


Superman 23

By:   	Scott Lobdell, Kenneth Rocafort	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Series:   	Superman
Publisher:   	DC Comics	
Pub. Date:  	August 28, 2013
Format:         CBZ

The "Psi-War" epic begins!

Psi-War erupts as Hector Hammond tries to take control of H.I.V.E. from its queen, but there are other forces in play as well, as a new Psycho Pirate emerges, and Superman is caught in the middle, unable to protect those closest to him
